To be able to change a variable to a component the variable in the component has to be marked with @Input before the variable so it can receive changes.
The normal synthesis would be something like &ltapp-theappname variableName = "the value i want to give it"&gt&lt/app-theappname> .
But with some variables like in this example boolean if you use the same synthesis you would get an error , here is how to get it working:

<div class="code-obj"><pre class="prettyprint linenums codeContainer"> 
